      <p><span class="sub-heading"><strong>Insurance:</strong></span></p>
      <blockquote>As  a rule we <strong>highly recommend</strong> our  passengers to arrange <strong>comprehensive</strong> <strong>travel insurance</strong> once booked for a tour  to cover all possible losses, injuries, cancellations, etc.*<br />
